title: [O level] English Oral topics : r/SGExams - Reddit
body: Wᴇʟᴄᴏᴍᴇ ᴛᴏ ʀ/SGExᴀᴍs - the largest community on reddit discussing education and student life in Singapore! SGExams is also more than a subreddit - we're a registered nonprofit that organises initiatives supporting students' academics, career guidance, mental health and holistic development, such as webinars and mentorship programmes.
